          "reviewBody": "My daughter was in TIGPS Garia since past 12 years . A strong bond of love and camaraderie has grown over the years. The teachers are extremely cordial and supportive . They bring the best out of every student. Principal Ma’am Mrs Tania Sen is very humble,  thoughtful and efficient administrator. She along with the teachers is  making an all round noteworthy development. We as guardians feel really proud and comfortable to have sent my daughter to an institution whereby she got an area of thinking in not just studies but other co-curriculars . I hope for the best of the school.🙏",
