          "reviewBody": "An excellent institution in South Kolkata offering best education, educational system and appreciably notable culture and discipline with affordable fees. It is an C.B.S.E affiliated school from Nursery to XII with the required educational amenities and infrastructure for the students. The school has got a new momentum due to the efforts of current Principal madam.Teachers are very cooperative and very helpful and supportive. Academic achievement and performance of the school are always notably very good.",
